Stacey Sheston is an alumna of the UC Davis School of Law currently working for McDonough Holland & Allen PC, specializing in public law.Footnote(Orio, Shelly. http://www.sacbar.org/members/saclawyer/mar_apr2005/sheston.html Attorney by Day, Band Member by Night. Sacramento Bar Association Magazine. Mar/Apr 2005.) She was a founding member of Natalie Cortez & the Ultra Violets, with whom she played bass, and now plays drums with The Essentials.
